These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Job: musician, architect, social-worker, accountant
Nationality: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. Nationality:egyptian is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1
2. Job:musician == Nationality:turkish##1
3. Nationality:thai is on the right of Nationality:chinese##1
4. Job:architect is on the left of Nationality:turkish##1
5. Job:accountant is on the left of Nationality:chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Job          | accountant | social-worker | architect | musician   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
Nationality: german, brazilian, nigerian, australian
1. Hobby:woodworking == Nationality:brazilian##1
2. Hobby:camping is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:cooking is on the right of Hobby:woodworking##1
4. Hobby:woodworking is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1
5. Nationality:brazilian is on the left of Nationality:german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | brazilian      | german | australian |

