.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
Color: apricot, fuchsia, azure, ivory
Movie-Genre: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the left of Movie-Genre:time-travel##1
2. Color:apricot == Movie-Genre:crime##1
3. Movie-Genre:drama is on the far right##1
4. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the right of Color:ivory##1
5. Color:azure is on the left of Movie-Genre:drama##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Color         | apricot | ivory | azure   | fuchsia |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

